sub_title: Lecturer & Researcher, Sustainable Development, social impact, social and frugal enterpreneurship, circular economy, evaluating impact.
summary:
Interested in the nexus of business and sustainable development; how private sector plays a role to creating impact and how the development sector can engage businesses. 

-Research Interests: sustainable development goals (SDGs), social impact, frugal innovation, circular economy, social enterprises. 
-Teaching: International Business, Comparative and cross-cultural management, Social & environmental entrepreneurship
